      "type": "structured",
      "totalMarks": 8,
      "difficulty": "medium",
      "context": "The table below shows some values of $y = x^2 - 3x + 2$ for $0 \\leq x \\leq 4$.\n\n| $x$ | 0 | 1 | 2 | 3 | 4 |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| $y$ | 2 | 0 | | | 6 |",
