            { "mark": "A1", "desc": "Smooth curve drawn through all five points in the correct domain" }
          ],
          "workingSteps": [
            "Plot all five points from the completed table",
            "Draw a smooth U-shaped curve"
          ]
        },
        {
          "label": "c",
          "questionText": "Use your graph to write down the values of $x$ for which $y = 0$.",
          "marks": 2,
